      ****************ENVIRONMENT DIVISION***************** 
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. P1.
       AUTHOR. GABRIELLA-DESTRO.
       DATE-WRITTEN. 14/05/2020. 
       DATE-COMPILED. 14/05/2020.
      *Este programa gera os arquivos aprov.dat e reprov.dat
      *copiando neles o arquivo alunos.dat

      ****************ENVIRONMENT DIVISION*****************  
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. PC.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. PC. 
       SPECIAL-NAMES. DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA. 
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT ALUNOS ASSIGN DISK
           ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
           SELECT APROV ASSIGN DISK
           ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
           SELECT REPROV ASSIGN DISK
           ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.

      ****************DATA DIVISION*****************  
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.

       FD ALUNOS 
       LABEL RECORDS STANDARD
           VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "ALUNOS.DAT".

       01 REGALUNO.       
           05 NUMALU PIC 9(6).
           05 NOMALU PIC X(20). 
           05 NOTALU PIC 9(2).

       FD APROV
       LABEL RECORDS STANDARD
           VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "APROV.DAT".

       01 REGAPROV. 
           05 NUMAP PIC 9(6).
           05 NOMAP PIC X(20). 
           05 CONCAP PIC X(1).

       FD REPROV
       LABEL RECORDS STANDARD
           VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "REPROV.DAT".

       01 REGREPROV. 
           05 NUMREP PIC 9(6).
           05 NOMREP PIC X(20). 
           05 CONCREP PIC X(1).

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       77  FIM PIC X VALUE SPACES.

      ****************PROCEDURE DIVISION*****************  
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.

       CONTROLE.
       PERFORM ABRIR.
       PERFORM LEITURA.
       PERFORM ROTINA UNTIL FIM EQUAL "*". 
       PERFORM FECHAR. 
       STOP RUN.


       ABRIR.
           OPEN INPUT ALUNOS 
                 OUTPUT APROV REPROV.

       LEITURA.
           READ ALUNOS
                 AT END MOVE "*" TO FIM. 

       ROTINA.
           PERFORM GRAVAR.
           PERFORM LEITURA.

       GRAVAR.
           MOVE NUMALU TO NUMAP.
           MOVE NUMALU TO NUMREP. 
           MOVE NOMALU TO NOMAP.
           MOVE NOMALU TO NOMREP.
           MOVE NOTALU TO CONCAP.
           MOVE NOTALU TO CONCREP.
           WRITE REGREPROV.
           WRITE REGAPROV.

       FECHAR.
           CLOSE ALUNOS APROV REPROV. 
           
           
           
          ------------------------
EXEMPLO DE ARQUIVO PARA ALUNOS.DAT:
          
123456 GABRIELLA DESTRO   10
